                     <interp inst="t18210411-160-person1609" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable - I saw the prisoner close to the prosecutor, but did not see him take the handkerchief - Jones took him with it in his hand - he made a great resistance.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210411-160-person1610">
